         <notesStmt>
            <note type="summary">After overcoming his sickness, Z. answers Kohen as he
                            had promised in ep. ZL00231. Regarding a question that arises from Sefer
                            de-Tsaniʿuta. Z. believes that the Novellae on the Zohar could Kohen in
                            the matter and he will instruct Samuel Hayyim to copy suitable texts for
                            him. Although he is preoccupied himself, he would like with Kohen to
                            help the community of Casale.</note>
            <note type="incipit" xml:lang="he">אמירי אמריך ישימירו את
                        </note>
